      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-cared for and drives like a dream! I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
