    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 power plant featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service, addressing critical E46 chassis and engine weak points. The 6-speed Getrag transmission provides precise engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via the factory M Variable Differential Lock. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers, ensuring the car tracks flat through high-lateral-G transitions. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, its mechanical integrity and linear power delivery remain uncompromising. A true driver\u2019s spec for those prioritizing tactile feedback and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
