      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained luxury sedan that perfectly balances executive comfort with spirited performance. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, and it shows in every detail. The exterior is finished in a stunning Obsidian Black that retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the lower front valance\u2014typical of careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the heated power seats and the crystal-clear premium audio system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule at authorized service centers, and I have the full maintenance history ready for your review. The engine runs smoothly and quietly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains firm yet compliant. With a fresh set of tires and recent brake service, this car is ready for the road with no immediate work required. It is a reliable, sophisticated vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
